<L>__{interior castle hackton various day and night}
<A>__{a few cuts showing mother keeping an eye on the countess.}
<C>__{roderick }
<D>__{yet i was bound to be on my guard that she should not give me the slip. had she left me, i was ruined the next day. i set my mother to keep sharp watch over the moods of her ladyship, and you may be sure that her assistance and surveillance were invaluable to me. if i had paid twenty spies to watch her lady, i should not have been half so well served as by the disinterested care and watchfulness of my excellent mother.}
